:"2021-01-31T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7714d86be82d9a4d103e60532feee584330a7b9","tid":2386691,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b263fbc679578523fea6bab4210e988c80d531b9","tid":2386691,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53a47e0589f0e3cba4d4477ddbdb359ac413f36","tid":2386691,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ff6090df0a79abdb77ad381c06ba02f4ee3d11","tid":2386691,"uid":279463,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"歌詞:<br />\n<br />\n與Catherine見了面 講起舊日每天<br />\n談及她過去 已封印 那未實現心願<br />\n回頭若 從頭又再選 餘生可會扭轉<br />\n時間是直行 哪會被重演<br />\n<br />\n與好知己見了面 想起近日變遷<br />\n無望的永遠 眾生裡 再踏步又一段<br />\n而來日 假使再看 這天應該怎麼算<br />\n才會令誓言 潔白地無損<br />\n<br />\n若盡了力 跑到累了<br />\n無力到 往往細碎沒法一一照料<br />\n平常心 好好的笑 好好的心跳<br />\n捱過夜晚 在那下秒 永遠也是破曉<br />\n<br />\n為何人們 親手將珍惜美夢粉碎<br />\n為何河流 被染污掉藍眼淚<br />\n誰人嚷着撤退 誰人投降 誰人熟睡<br />\n願我去到終端 能堅守未被壓碎<br />\n才能漠視傀儡 才能頑強<br />\n才能辨別哪一句是對<br />\n<br />\n社會公式去訓練 思想現實了點<br />\n無望的永遠 眾生裡 更混亂又一段<br />\n而來日 假使再看 這天應該怎麼算<br />\n才會令善良 潔白地無損<br />\n<br />\n若盡了力 跑到累了<br />\n無力到 往往細碎沒法一一照料<br />\n平常心 好好的笑 好好的心跳<br />\n捱過夜晚 在那下秒 永遠也是破曉<br />\n<br />\n為何人們 親手將珍惜美夢粉碎<br />\n為何河流 被染污掉藍眼淚<br />\n人人嚷着撤退 人人投降 人人熟睡<br />\n未免也會心虛 難保今夜被壓碎<br />\n成王或敗寇裡 仍然無名<br />\n仍然認定我不會後退<br />\n<br />\n請不要顧慮 誣蔑我的幾千個控罪<br />\n請不要別去 縱使問題一堆<br />\n請真摰地面對 要信守 信念抱緊揮之不去<br />\n上善如水 分開會再聚<br />\n<br />\n為何人們 親手將珍惜美夢粉碎<br />\n為何河流 被染污掉藍眼淚<br />\n誰人嚷着撤退 誰人投降 誰人熟睡<br />\n願我去到終端 能堅守未被壓碎<br />\n才能漠視傀儡 才能頑強<br />\n才能辨別哪一句是對<br />\n<br />\n如何難行 當只得這一個夢相隨<br />\n如何徬徨 沒了頂是藍眼淚<br />\n人人嚷着撤退 人人投降 人人熟睡<br />\n歷過世界興衰 留低的未被壓碎<br />\n成王或敗寇裡 仍然無名<br />\n仍然認定我不會後退<br />\n才能傲視傀儡 才能頑強<br />\n才能定義我的對是對<br />\n<br />\nspotify都有! <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/7q83AMYByTqWciO6oemA0q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Falbum%2F7q83AMYByTqWciO6oemA0q&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=1e792639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/album/7q83AMYByTqWciO6oemA0q</a>"},{"pid":"fcfc186518dcfecab0e74f396b2ebb4eceea278e","tid":2386691,"uid":387391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"幾時今天我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86b385d3d4c56bd11ec982cf61b05f90dacf447","tid":2386691,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b288f5b0098bd5bfd5fef0987ca35d9d6820cec","tid":2386691,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e01152915ccc71c20bb700fd4c8b2b8f33a51f1","tid":2386691,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:41: